"35:28:13" : {s: 35, a: 28, w: 13, r: "علم", t: "ٱلْعُلَمَٰٓؤُا۟", l: "عَلِيم", lc: 163, tl: "l-ʿulamāu", lb: "পরম জ্ঞানী ",e: "those who have knowledge", b: "আলেমগণ, জ্ঞানীরা", f: 1, rm: "to mark/sign/distinguish, creations/beings, world, science/learning/knowledge/information, aware/know. By means of which one knows a thing, hence it signifies world or creation, because by it the Creator is known. alim (pl. ulama) - one who is learned/wise or knows."},
