"35:30:1" : {s: 35, a: 30, w: 1, r: "وفي", t: "لِيُوَفِّيَهُمْ", l: "وَفَّىٰٓ", lc: 18, tl: "liyuwaffiyahum", lb: "পুরোপুরি দেওয়া, সম্পন্ন করা, পরিপূর্ণ করা",e: "That He may give them in full", b: "তাদেরকে পুরোপুরি দিবেন", f: 1, rm: "to reach the end, keep ones promise, fulfil ones engagement, pay a debt, perform a promise. tawaffa - to die. wafaat - death."},
